## MANDATORY CONTENT GUIDELINES

### Cultural Heritage
- Present Funan Kingdom as SHARED Southeast Asian heritage
- NEVER claim specific cultural elements belong to one country
- Use fictional names for all locations (not real temple names)
- Use fictional names for all historical figures (not real king names)
- Frame cultural elements as "ancient Funan" not "Khmer" or "Thai"

### Temple and Sacred Site Depiction
- DO NOT use exact replicas of Angkor Wat, Preah Vihear, or other UNESCO sites
- Create "inspired by" architecture, not copies
- Temples in game should be fictional "Funan Temple" style
- No destruction of temple structures in gameplay
- Respectful exploration only

### Character Design
- Animal characters avoid ethnic representation issues (GOOD)
- If human characters, use diverse/neutral skin tones
- Avoid ethnic stereotypes
- Apsara dancers: elegant and respectful, not sexualized
- Traditional dress: respectful representation

### Religious Elements
- Hindu-Buddhist blend is historically accurate for Funan (GOOD)
- Nagas, dragons, mythological creatures are safe
- Deities should be depicted respectfully
- Religious ceremonies shown as beautiful/educational
- No mockery of religious practices

