## REQUIRED DISCLAIMERS

### Main Disclaimer (Required in game)
Include this text in the game's opening, about section, and app store description:

```
"What the Funan" is a work of fiction inspired by the ancient Funan Kingdom 
(1st-9th Century CE). All characters, events, and locations are fictional. 
Any resemblance to real historical figures is coincidental. This game 
celebrates the shared cultural heritage of Southeast Asia and is created 
with respect for all cultures and traditions depicted.
```

### Educational Disclaimer
```
This game contains educational content about ancient Southeast Asian history. 
Representations of religious and cultural elements are intended to be 
respectful and educational.
```

