## DATA PROTECTION REQUIREMENTS

### Thailand PDPA Compliance
- Obtain explicit consent before collecting personal data
- For users under 20: require parental/guardian consent
- Provide clear privacy policy in Thai language
- Allow data export and deletion requests
- Secure storage of all personal data

### COPPA Compliance (Children's Game)
- No collection of personal data from children under 13 without parental consent
- Implement age gate at first launch
- Parental gate for purchases
- No behavioral advertising to children

### GDPR Compliance
- Right to be forgotten
- Data portability
- Clear consent mechanisms
- Privacy by design

